        "text": "received testimony, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "of God’s approbation of them, or were borne witnesses to by God as persons accepted of him. The word is very comprehensive, implying that God gave a testimony, not only ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "of ",
        "children": []
