      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "them, but ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "to ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "them, and they received his testimony, as if it had been the things themselves, of which he testified, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Hebrews 11:4-5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Hebrews 11:39",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Hence they also gave testimony to others, and others testified of them. This chapter is a kind of summary of the Old Testament, in which the apostle comprises the designs, labours, sojournings, expectations, martyrdoms of the ancients. The former of them had a long exercise of their patience; the latter suffered shorter, but sharper trials.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
