      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For by it the elders obtained a good report",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Lit., “For therein the elders had witness borne to them.” Their “good report” was won in the sphere of faith. The elders—a technical Jewish term (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
